---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Base.astro';
import Navbar from '@/components/global/header/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '@/components/global/Footer.astro';
import Reveal from '@/components/widgets/Reveal.astro';
import { generatePaths } from '@/lib/utils/i18nUtils';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';

export function getStaticPaths() {
  return generatePaths();
}

const shareLinks = [
  { label: 'Facebook', icon: 'lucide:facebook' },
  { label: 'X', icon: 'lucide:twitter' },
  { label: 'LinkedIn', icon: 'lucide:linkedin' },
  { label: 'Vimeo', icon: 'lucide:video' },
];

const selectorList = [
  'Type selector (e.g p, span, etc.)',
  'Class selector (e.g .element, .sidebar, etc.)',
  'ID selector (e.g #header)',
];

const tags = ['Blog', 'Creative', 'Portfolio', 'Theme', 'WordPress'];

const comments = [
  {
    author: 'By James Taylor',
    date: 'January 2, 2024',
    body: "I love this theme. Sometimes it's difficult to work with some themes, because even if they are created with Elementor, you can't edit all the things with Elementor.",
  },
  {
    author: 'By Oliver Williams',
    date: 'January 2, 2024',
    body: 'They have really taken their time to work on the appearance of the theme, also, they have a very interactive client assistance service, I like it!',
  },
];
---

<Layout title="Control your online banking while earning rewards — Zylo Blog" description="Resources article from Zylo on online banking, rewards, and modern product engineering.">
  <Navbar />

  <main id="main" class="pt-32 pb-24 bg-slate-50/50">
    <div class="container-page max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      {/* 1. Header */}
      <Reveal class="mb-10">
        <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-brand hover:underline mb-6">
          <Icon name="lucide:arrow-left" class="w-4 h-4" /> Back to blog
        </a>
        <span class="inline-block border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold text-slate-800 uppercase tracking-wider mb-6 shadow-sm">
          Resources
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 font-heading tracking-tight leading-tight">
          Control your online banking while earning rewards.
        </h1>
      </Reveal>

      {/* 2. Author + share */}
      <Reveal delay={80} class="mb-12">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-6 pb-8 border-b border-slate-200">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-brand text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold font-heading text-xl">
              R
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 font-heading">Richard</h2>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Community Organiser</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
            {shareLinks.map((s) => (
              <a
                href="#"
                aria-label={s.label}
                class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white text-slate-700 hover:border-brand/40 hover:text-brand transition-colors"
              >
                <Icon name={s.icon} class="w-4 h-4" />
              </a>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </Reveal>

      {/* 3. Article body */}
      <Reveal delay={120} class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 md:p-12 shadow-sm text-slate-700 leading-relaxed text-base mb-12">
        <p class="mb-6">
          We love to bring designs to life as a developer, and I aim to do this using whatever front end tools
          are necessary. My preferred tools are more modern javascript libraries like React.js but I like to use
          whatever is best for the websites needs. There are several reasons why a business would consider
          a rebrand and it doesn&rsquo;t necessarily mean the business has been unsuccessful.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-10">
          But in order that you may see whence all this born error of those who accuse pleasure and praise
          pain, I will open the whole matter, and explain the very things which were said by that discoverer of
          truth and, as it were, the architect of a happy life.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 font-heading mb-4">Using a Query</h2>
        <p class="mb-10">
          We love to bring designs to life as a developer, and I aim to do this using whatever front end tools are
          necessary. My preferred tools are more modern javascript libraries like React.js but I like to use
          whatever is best for the websites needs. There are several reasons why a business would consider a
          rebrand and it doesn&rsquo;t necessarily mean the business has been unsuccessful.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-10">
          Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus enim. In aliquam tempus porta. Mauris vel finibus risus.
          Maecenas egestas mi sed neque finibus, nec faucibus ipsum aliquet. Duis scelerisque at odio vel
          tempus. Morbi a tincidunt nunc, id rutrum erat. Fusce egestas quam vel facilisis tempor. Morbi non
          orci elementum, sollicitudin mauris laoreet, luctus est. Donec in mi lorem.
        </p>

        <div class="flex items-start gap-6 mb-10">
          <Icon name="lucide:quote" class="w-10 h-10 text-brand flex-none" />
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <blockquote class="text-slate-900 text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold font-heading leading-snug tracking-tight">
              &ldquo;Success is the result of perfection, hard work, learning from failure, loyalty, &amp;
              persistence&rdquo;
            </blockquote>
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500">Phil Martinez</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="mb-10">
          Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus enim. In aliquam tempus porta. Mauris vel finibus risus.
          Maecenas egestas mi sed neque finibus, nec faucibus ipsum aliquet. Duis scelerisque at odio vel
          tempus. Morbi a tincidunt nunc, id rutrum erat. Fusce egestas quam vel facilisis tempor. Morbi non
          orci elementum, sollicitudin mauris laoreet, luctus est. Donec in mi lorem.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 font-heading mb-4">On the specificity of selectors</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
          The specificity of the : <span class="text-brand font-semibold">not()</span> pseudo-class is the
          specificity of its argument. The :not() pseudo-class does not add to the selector specificity, unlike
          other pseudo-classes.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-6">
          The <span class="text-brand font-semibold">simple selector</span> that:
          <span class="text-brand font-semibold">not()</span> takes as an argument can be any of the following:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2.5 mb-10">
          {selectorList.map((item) => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <Icon name="lucide:check" class="w-4 h-4 text-brand mt-1 flex-none" />
              <span>{item}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <Icon name="lucide:check" class="w-4 h-4 text-brand mt-1 flex-none" />
            <span>
              Pseudo-class selector e.g: <span class="text-brand font-semibold">first-child, :last-of-type</span>
            </span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50/50 p-6 md:p-8 font-mono text-sm text-slate-700 mb-10">
          <div>{'li:not(.old)::after {'}</div>
          <div class="pl-8 my-2">
            <div>{'content: "New!";'}</div>
            <div>{'color: deepPink;'}</div>
          </div>
          <div>{'}'}</div>
        </div>

        <p>
          The specificity of the : <span class="text-brand font-semibold">not()</span> pseudo-class is the
          specificity of its argument. The :not() pseudo-class does not add to the selector specificity, unlike
          other pseudo-classes.
        </p>
      </Reveal>

      {/* 4. Tags */}
      <Reveal delay={140} class="mb-12">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 text-sm">
          <span class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mr-1">Tagged with:</span>
          {tags.map((t) => (
            <a
              href="#"
              class="px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white text-slate-600 hover:border-brand/40 hover:text-brand transition-colors"
            >
              {t}
            </a>
          ))}
        </div>
      </Reveal>

      {/* 5. About Author */}
      <Reveal delay={160} class="mb-12">
        <div class="rounded-3xl bg-slate-900 p-8 md:p-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center sm:items-start gap-6 text-center sm:text-left">
          <div class="w-24 h-24 flex-none rounded-full bg-brand text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold font-heading text-2xl">
            PB
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
            <div>
              <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400 tracking-wide">About Author</span>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white font-heading mt-1">Peter Bowman</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-slate-300 text-base leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
              Phasellus et ipsum justo. Aenean fringilla a fermentum mauris non venenatis. Praesent at nulla
              aliquam ligula.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center sm:justify-start gap-4 mt-1 text-slate-400">
              {shareLinks.map((s) => (
                <a href="#" aria-label={s.label} class="hover:text-white transition-colors">
                  <Icon name={s.icon} class="w-4 h-4" />
                </a>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </Reveal>

      {/* 6. Next Post */}
      <Reveal delay={180} class="mb-12">
        <a
          href="/article"
          class="group block rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm hover:border-brand/40 hover:shadow-lg transition-all"
        >
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold text-brand uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">
            Next Post <Icon name="lucide:arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4" />
          </span>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 font-heading tracking-tight group-hover:text-brand transition-colors">
            Tips for thriving in our virtual world
          </h3>
        </a>
      </Reveal>

      {/* 7. Comments */}
      <Reveal delay={200} class="mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 font-heading mb-6">Comments(02)</h3>
        <div class="space-y-5">
          {comments.map((c) => (
            <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm">
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                <h4 class="text-base font-bold text-slate-900 font-heading">{c.author}</h4>
                <span class="text-xs text-slate-400">{c.date}</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">{c.body}</p>
              <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold text-brand hover:underline">
                Reply <Icon name="lucide:corner-down-left" class="w-4 h-4" />
              </a>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </Reveal>

      {/* 8. Leave a Reply */}
      <Reveal delay={220}>
        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 md:p-12 shadow-sm">
          <div class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 font-heading tracking-tight mb-2">
              Leave a Reply
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
              Your email address will not be published. Required fields are marked *
            </p>
          </div>

          <form class="space-y-6">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                <label for="name" class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Name *</label>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="name"
                  required
                  class="w-full px-5 py-3.5 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-full text-slate-900 focus:outline-none focus:border-brand focus:ring-1 focus:ring-brand transition-all"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                <label for="email" class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Email*</label>
                <input
                  type="email"
                  id="email"
                  required
                  class="w-full px-5 py-3.5 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-full text-slate-900 focus:outline-none focus:border-brand focus:ring-1 focus:ring-brand transition-all"
                />
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
              <label for="website" class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Website</label>
              <input
                type="url"
                id="website"
                class="w-full px-5 py-3.5 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-full text-slate-900 focus:outline-none focus:border-brand focus:ring-1 focus:ring-brand transition-all"
              />
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
              <label for="comment" class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Comment *</label>
              <textarea
                id="comment"
                rows="6"
                required
                class="w-full px-5 py-4 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-3xl text-slate-900 resize-none focus:outline-none focus:border-brand focus:ring-1 focus:ring-brand transition-all"></textarea>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-3 pt-2">
              <input id="checkbox" type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 rounded border-slate-300 text-brand focus:ring-brand" />
              <label for="checkbox" class="text-sm text-slate-600 cursor-pointer">
                Save my name, email, and website in this browser for the next time I comment.
              </label>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-4">
              <button
                type="submit"
                class="inline-flex h-12 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-slate-900 px-8 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-brand transition-colors shadow-md"
              >
                Post comment <Icon name="lucide:send" class="w-4 h-4" />
              </button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </Reveal>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
